custom_1732109739705.name: Funny Shit
custom_1732109739705.description: Characterized by wildly exaggerated proportions where objects and figures are either comically oversized or hilariously tiny, with vibrant, clashing colors creating a visual cacophony, surreal combinations of unrelated elements that defy logic, chaotic and unpredictable compositions that feel deliberately nonsensical, and an overarching sense of playful absurdity designed to elicit laughter, confusion, and sheer delight in its unapologetically over-the-top ridiculousness

custom_1732173392178.name: Typography
custom_1732173392178.description: Merging bold typography with vibrant, retro-inspired illustrations, it creates a visually striking narrative where text and imagery seamlessly intertwine. Overlapping layers, geometric shapes, and a nostalgic yet modern color palette evoke a sense of depth and movement. The composition is dynamic and complex, with every element—from the characters to symbols—working together to form a cohesive, story-driven design. Playful yet sophisticated, it balances intricate details with bold, impactful visuals

custom_1732185184860.name: Video Game
custom_1732185184860.description: A video game-inspired style features slightly angular 3D models with geometric details, blending nostalgic low-poly aesthetics with a modern, minimalist twist. Models showcase simplified edges and visible polygons reminiscent of early 3D games, enhanced with high-resolution textures and subtle gradients. The color palette is vibrant and contrasting, often incorporating lighting effects like neon glows and reflections to create a dynamic, immersive atmosphere. This style captures a mix of retro charm and futuristic design, focusing on visual clarity and playability
